'''archive.today'''又称'''archive.is'''，是一個私人資助的网页存档網站，<ref name="freecomtw">{{cite web|url = https://free.com.tw/archive-is/|title = Archive.is 線上備份網頁工具，可下載完整網頁內容或將畫面轉為擷圖|publisher = Free.co.tw|author = pseric|date = 2015-06-27|accessdate = 2015-07-26|archive-date = 2015-06-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150627114314/https://free.com.tw/archive-is/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="cnet">{{cite web|url = http://www.ghacks.net/2015/04/22/create-publicly-available-web-page-archives-with-archive-is/|title = Create publicly available web page archives with archive.is|publisher = {{tsl|en|GHacks|}}|author = Martin Brinkmann|date = 2015-04-22|accessdate = 2015-06-13|archive-date = 2015-10-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151012113129/http://www.ghacks.net/2015/04/22/create-publicly-available-web-page-archives-with-archive-is/|dead-url = yes}}</ref>資料中心位於歐洲法國的[[北部-加来海峡|北部-加来海峡]]。<ref name="statradar">{{cite web|url = http://www.statradar.com/www/archive.is|title = archive.is status|publisher = Stat Radar|accessdate = 2013-05-08|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130727194719/http://www.statradar.com/www/archive.is|archivedate = 2013-07-27|deadurl = yes}}</ref>這個{{le|網站典藏|Web archiving}}檔案館使用[[Apache_Hadoop|Apache Hadoop]]與{{le|Apache Accumulo|Apache Accumulo}}軟體。它可以一次取回一個類似於[[WebCite|WebCite]]的小於50MB的頁面，並能收錄[[Google地圖|Google地圖]]與[[Twitter|Twitter]]。<span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="69"></span>

archive.is会根据版權所有者的合乎[[數位千年版權法案|數位千年版權法案]]（DMCA）的撤除請求移除已存檔的頁面。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.archive.is/post/41395737942/how-can-i-delete-an-archived-page |title="How can I delete an archived page?" |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archive-date=2015-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721011357/http://blog.archive.is/post/41395737942/how-can-i-delete-an-archived-page |dead-url=no }}</ref>

它每次請求都會擷取網頁的文字內容，載入不含活動元素或指令碼的[[Web_2.0|Web 2.0]]網站或由[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]產生的圖片與框架內容。 截圖是1024×768像素，沒有快顯畫面。<ref name="archive.today">{{cite web|url = http://archive.today/|title = archive.today – webpage capture|publisher = archive.today|accessdate = 2013-05-08|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120628130627/http://archive.today/|archivedate = 2012-06-28|deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="archive.today faq">{{cite web|url = http://archive.is/faq.html|title = archive.today FAQ|publisher = archive.today|accessdate = 2013-05-08|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130420053326/http://archive.is/faq.html|archivedate = 2013-04-20|deadurl = yes}}</ref>

截至2015年，archive.is還支援了{{le|Memento Project|Memento Project}}的[[API|API]]，<ref name=WSRG>{{cite web |url=http://ws-dl.blogspot.nl/2013/07/2013-07-09-archiveis-supports-memento.html |title=Archive.is Supports Memento |publisher=Web Science and Digital Libraries Research Group at [[老道明大學|Old Dominion University]] |work=Research and Teaching Updates |date=2013-07-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130727194715/http://ws-dl.blogspot.de/2013/07/2013-07-09-archiveis-supports-memento.html |archivedate=2013-07-27 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-09-17 |first=Michael L. |last=Nelson }}</ref><ref>[http://mementoweb.org/depot/native/archiveis/ "archive.is"] {{Wayback|url=http://mementoweb.org/depot/native/archiveis/ |date=20150703022520 }} ''Memento Protocol Information''. Memento Development Group. Retrieved 17 September 2013.</ref>並且開發了Firefox瀏覽器<ref>{{cite web|url=https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/archiveror/|title=Archiveror – Get this Extension for 🦊 Firefox (en-US)|website=addons.mozilla.org|accessdate=2019-06-29|archive-date=2019-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190625172159/https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/archiveror/|dead-url=no}}</ref>與Chrome瀏覽器<ref>{{cite web|url=https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/archivetoday-button/cgjpabpjaocpgppajkeplhbipbdippdm|title=archive.today Button|website=chrome.google.com|accessdate=2019-06-29|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629061246/https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/archivetoday-button/cgjpabpjaocpgppajkeplhbipbdippdm|dead-url=no}}</ref>的[[瀏覽器擴充功能|擴充功能]]。

== 封鎖 ==
在2015年7月21日，網站管理人員封鎖了[[芬蘭|芬蘭]]的IP位址，他们在其Twitter上聲稱，这麼做是為了避免與芬蘭政府的糾紛升級。他們拒絕提供額外的資訊。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/archiveis/status/623524336184524800|title=@FukBoyKuupe @atlasnodded  I blocked proactively in order not to escalate as in recent Russia vs. http://archive.org   case.|first=|last=archive.today|date=2015-07-21|publisher=|accessdate=2015-07-22|archive-date=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151021152057/https://twitter.com/archiveis/status/623524336184524800|dead-url=no}}</ref>此網站也被中国<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.greatfire.org/archive.is|title=archive.is is 100% blocked in China|date=12 August 2018|website=GreatFire Analyzer|archive-url=https://archive.today/20180812150852/https://en.greatfire.org/https/archive.is|archive-date=12 August 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>與[[哈薩克斯坦|哈薩克斯坦]]封鎖。此站同樣被[[OpenDNS|OpenDNS]]封鎖。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/jaredallard/status/624587735982944256|title=Even my school blocks http://archive.today , what the hell|first=|last=Jared|date=2015-07-24|publisher=|accessdate=2019-06-29|archive-date=2018-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181228225908/https://twitter.com/jaredallard/status/624587735982944256|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 易名 ==
archive.is曾多次更換網域名稱。

從建站初期至2014年4月14日是使用「Archive[[.is|.is]]」（首字母為大寫）。

在2014年4月15日時，該網站的名稱已更名為「archive[[.today|.today]]」（首字母為小寫）。<ref>[http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/custom?inlang=ja&client=pub-&hl=ja&q=cache:iKUcXEywpPAJ:http://archive.is/ archive.is - webpage capture] - [[Google|Google]] 2014年4月14日 11:21:06 GMT （[http://megalodon.jp/2014-0420-2143-48/www.peeep.us/66ce5100 Peeep.usのキャッシュ] {{Wayback|url=http://megalodon.jp/2014-0420-2143-48/www.peeep.us/66ce5100 |date=20150701013443 }}）</ref><ref>[http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/custom?inlang=ja&client=pub-&hl=ja&q=cache:rneU7V6weTIJ:http://archive.is/ archive.today - webpage capture] - [[Google|Google]] 2014年4月18日 17:40:45 GMT （[http://megalodon.jp/2014-0420-2142-46/www.peeep.us/912f1ddb Peeep.usのキャッシュ] {{Wayback|url=http://megalodon.jp/2014-0420-2142-46/www.peeep.us/912f1ddb |date=20150701023449 }}）</ref>

在2015年春季又改回了「archive.is」（首字母為小寫）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://megalodon.jp/2015-0322-2249-26/https://archive.today:443/|title=https://archive.today:443/ - 2015年3月22日 22:49 - ウェブ魚拓|work=megalodon.jp|accessdate=2015年7月19日|archive-date=2015年6月28日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150628005311/http://megalodon.jp/2015-0322-2249-26/https://archive.today:443/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://megalodon.jp/2015-0514-0108-01/https://archive.is:443/|title=https://archive.is:443/ - 2015年5月14日 01:08 - ウェブ魚拓|work=megalodon.jp|accessdate=2015年7月19日|archive-date=2015年6月28日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150628005401/http://megalodon.jp/2015-0514-0108-01/https://archive.is:443/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年夏季，此网站采用「archive.today」为标题，主域名替换为「archive[[.ph|.ph]]」。

== 使用案例 ==
這個檔案館会被一些作者或{{le|駭客活動分子|hacktivists}}使用。
* 有些在线用户（例如[[玩家门|玩家门]]成員）使用它查看他们反对的网站的内容以避免向其贡献[[网站流量|网站流量]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/ypw5mj/dear-gamergate-please-stop-stealing-our-shit|title=Dear GamerGate: Please Stop Stealing Our Shit|first=Jason|last=Koebler|date=2014-10-29|publisher=|accessdate=2019-06-29|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629061250/https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/ypw5mj/dear-gamergate-please-stop-stealing-our-shit|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* [[朱利安·阿桑奇|朱利安·阿桑奇]]《當Google遇上維基解密》（''When Google Met WikiLeaks''）的一書中<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://pdf.yt/d/iZiFQpms8I1pKFs7 |title=Julian Assange - When Google Met WikiLeaks |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archive-date=2015-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721012534/https://pdf.yt/d/iZiFQpms8I1pKFs7 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>使用了archive.is保留線上引文。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://wikileaks.org/google-is-not-what-it-seems/#ftn1|title=Julian Assange - Google Is Not What It Seems|first=Debian|last=user|date=2014-10-24|accessdate=2015-07-17|archive-date=2016-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114080401/https://wikileaks.org/google-is-not-what-it-seems/#ftn1|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* {{le|叙利亚电子军|Syrian Electronic Army}}為了證明他們入侵網站而使用它。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://sea.sy/article/id/2083/en|date = 2015-06-14|title = US Army Official Website Hacked — Syrian Electronic Army|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150611183944/http://sea.sy/article/id/2083/en|archivedate = 2015-06-11|deadurl = yes|accessdate = 2015-07-17}}</ref>

== 評論 ==
有別於比如[[網際網路檔案館|網際網路檔案館時光機]]（''Internet Archive Wayback Machine''）的主动性[[網路蜘蛛|網路蜘蛛]]，archive.is每次只擷取網站的一個頁面，所以不遵守「[[Robots.txt|Robots排除標準]]」。 <ref>{{cite web|first = Dan|last = Dascalescu|url = http://wiki.dandascalescu.com/reviews/online_services/web_page_archiving|title = Web page archiving - Dan Dascalescu's Wiki (review)|publisher = Wiki.dandascalescu.com|date = 2013-02-18|accessdate = 2013-10-03|archive-date = 2015-10-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151012114513/http://wiki.dandascalescu.com/reviews/online_services/web_page_archiving|dead-url = yes}}</ref>

{{quote|從法律上講，archive.today與網際網路檔案館時光機有很大不同。互联网档案馆的时光机抓取网页时遵循通常的Robots指令，这种指令可以阻止其抓取特定的网页。然而，网站无法阻止archive.today的用户对其制作站点镜像。|sign = Jason Koebler | source = [http://motherboard.vice.com/read/dear-gamergate-please-stop-stealing-our-shit Dear GamerGate: Please Stop Stealing Our Shit]}}

